access: You have the entire studio to yourself!
description:
* 5 minute walk to train station (Trains to NYC - F, E, R and 7) 

* Bus behind studio takes you directly to the city too!

*FREE WIFI

*Flat screen TV, Full size fridge, microwave, kitchen, coffee maker, private bathroom

*10 mins from LGA & 20 mins from JFK!

* Safe neighborhood 

*Laundry & Dryer available for 1 wk + stays

*Lots of restaurants - Greek, Italian, Spanish, French, Asian, supermarket and pharmacy stores all walking distance from studio.

*Easy Parking on the street

The Studio has a separate private entrance. It's cozy and TV is mounted so you can watch it from the comfort of your bed, the couch, the dining room or the kitchen.

You have the entire studio to yourself!

As being a New Yorker my whole life I can guide you and give you great tips on discounts and attractions around the city. Se habla Espanol.

We're located in the great diverse Borough of Queens, minutes away from NYC. Safe neighborhood with private houses all around. We have a lot of transportation around the Studio just walking distance - Bus in the corner, metro train 4 blocks away!

Bus stop in the corner of the house and major NYC trains a couple of blocks away. Trains - R, F, E, 7

The Studio is 5 minutes away from La Guardia Airport and 20 minutes from JFK.

hosts.about:
Hi everyone,

We're the Londahl Family : )
We have a place in New York and a place in Bogota, Colombia where we like to welcome guests from all over the world! 
My husband is American/German and I was born in Colombia but raised in the U.S. since the age of 10. We love meeting people from different places and building new friendships : )
We put a lot of love in our two apartments and hope you enjoy your stay with us to the fullest!

- we speak English and Espanol

review.comments: Appartamento pulito, ben equipaggiato, acqua sempre calda.. proprietari gentilissimi e ben disponibili a soddisfare le richieste dei loro ospiti. Ben collegato con i mezzi di trasporto (bus e subway) che ti conducono nel centro della città e in periferia. Nelle sue vicinanze supermarket, ristoranti, lavanderia.....un posto sicuramente da consigliare!!!
